You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Firestarter and The Adrenaline Rush vibe.

The The Adrenaline Rush vibe means Heart-racing, full-body intensity, unpredictable challenges. This is especially good for Those who crave challenge, variety, and adrenaline..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
